Source: libdrm
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Debian X Strike Force <debian-x@lists.debian.org>
Uploaders: Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>, David Nusinow <dnusinow@debian.org>, Brice Goglin <bgoglin@debian.org>
